Package: restatis
Title: R Wrapper for the GENESIS Web Service RESTful API of the German
    Federal Statistical Office (Statistisches Bundesamt/Destatis)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yannik", "Buhl", role = "aut"),
    person("Zoran", "Kovacevic", role = "aut",
